# Brain stores survey

This is the flagg snapshot from 2026-07-17 10:01 PDT. The filesystem was
active while I surveyed it, so counts are a point-in-time receipt, not a
promise that writers stopped.

## What exists on flagg

The required scan found **31 `.brain` trees**, containing **2,027 `.svx` pages**
and **29 `.md` files**. The registry names four roots. Everything else is an
orphan from the wiki's point of view, not automatically a mistake.

`~/.brain` is not a fifth store. It is a symlink to
`~/Code/joelhooks/dark-wizard/.brain`, the registered `user` root.

